# Development Environment

- Use these existing development URLs:
  - Development server is running at: http://localhost:3001
  - Storybook is running at: http://localhost:7000
  - DO NOT start new server instances
- Project structure:
  - src/components/: atoms, molecules, organisms, layout
  - src/context/: React Context providers
  - src/hooks/: Custom React hooks
  - src/utils/: Utilities
  - src/styles/: Global styles
- Environment requirements:
  - Node.js v22+
  - Yarn v1.22+
  - Port 3001: Reserved for running dev server
  - Port 7000: Reserved for running Storybook
- Development tools:
  - Use existing Vite dev server instance
  - Use existing Storybook instance
  - TypeScript compiler
  - ESLint + Prettier
  - Vitest watch mode